Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.00,0:01:36.32,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,One day, a large number of Hollows\Nsuddenly appeared in Karakura Town.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.04,0:01:39.40,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo and Rukia left\Nto exterminate the Hollows,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.44,0:01:42.78,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,and in the midst of battle,\Nthey encountered a strange trio.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.64,0:01:45.84,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Ishida and the others arrived to help,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.88,0:01:47.72,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,and the Hollows were\Npromptly dealt with.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.99,0:01:51.49,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo went after the strange trio\Nonly to find that they had disappeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.28,0:01:55.33,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,However, he meets them once more\Nin a totally unexpected place.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.88,0:01:59.16,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,They have moved in next door,\Nbehind the Kurosaki Clinic.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.99,0:02:01.24,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Furthermore, the following day,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.28,0:02:04.80,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,it turns out that they are\Nto be Ichigo’s classmates.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.80,0:02:07.77,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.80,0:02:09.77,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,She’s cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.48,0:02:17.48,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,He’s huge!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.32,0:02:21.32,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.40,0:02:22.40,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,A giant?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.72,0:02:25.08,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That girl has to be\Nin grade school!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.12,0:02:26.68,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Two adults and a child!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.92,0:02:29.24,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I am Kenryu.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.28,0:02:32.04,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,This man on my left is Enryu.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.32,0:02:35.24,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,And this person here is…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.60,0:02:40.71,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I am Rurichiyo Kasumiohji!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.32,0:02:42.71,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Pleased to make\Nyour acquaintance!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.68,0:02:45.13,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,– Huh?!\N– Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.04,0:02:52.96,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, Rurichiyo!\NWhere’d you move from?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.28,0:02:54.40,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Very far away.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.06,0:02:57.36,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,How come you three\Ntransferred together?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.77,0:02:58.92,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,We’re related.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.44,0:03:00.56,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Where do you live?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.44,0:03:02.29,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That’s a secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.48,0:03:03.96,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What’re your body measurements?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.52,0:03:07.00,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You even go after girls like her?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.00,0:03:09.50,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,But, she’s so cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.04,0:03:13.88,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,How come only you are answering\Nall the questions, Kenryu?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.04,0:03:16.32,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Lady Rurichiyo is a person\Nof high nobility.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.48,0:03:19.88,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It is a waste of her time\Nto reply to those beneath her.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.64,0:03:23.28,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Beneath her? Aw, come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.32,0:03:25.32,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Don’t exaggerate.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.53,0:03:27.97,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You there.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.72,0:03:31.36,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Do not get too friendly\Nwith Lady Rurichiyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.68,0:03:32.76,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.80,0:03:34.36,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,If you become too\Nfriendly with her…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.44,0:03:37.00,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,you’ll lose your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.40,0:03:38.64,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,N-No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.16,0:03:41.70,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, Ichigo…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.84,0:03:43.87,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.72,0:03:50.84,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What? How come she’ll talk to Ichigo,\Nbut I get threatened?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.32,0:03:54.81,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,F-Forget what I just said.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.95,0:03:58.65,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo! School is\Na strange place indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.76,0:04:00.85,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.22,0:04:03.29,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone is dressed alike.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.64,0:04:04.82,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Are they Soul Reapers?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.86,0:04:06.79,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.20,0:04:09.87,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Lady Rurichiyo is\Ndirectly addressing you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.20,0:04:12.10,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Answer more politely!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.92,0:04:16.76,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Not so close, guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.48,0:04:20.53,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo! I am thirsty.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.53,0:04:25.49,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, do you always talk like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.64,0:04:27.28,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Do I sound funny?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.28,0:04:29.61,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, this isn’t the feudal age.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.12,0:04:33.28,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,F-Forget what I just said.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.00,0:04:35.16,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,There’s nothing wrong\Nwith the way you speak.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.68,0:04:37.24,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,In fact, I like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.84,0:04:39.40,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,To each his own taste.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.40,0:04:42.26,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Yup, I think it’s cute too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.28,0:04:45.56,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Bring me something\Nto drink, Ichigo.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.80,0:04:47.80,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Why me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.36,0:04:53.12,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Go! Be grateful that Lady Rurichiyo\Nherself is ordering you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.12,0:04:54.37,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Why you…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.68,0:04:58.84,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on… Go buy her\Nsome juice at least, Ichigo.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.21,0:05:01.85,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Be kind to transfer students.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.19,0:05:03.76,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.56,0:05:07.64,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,This is getting to be a chore.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.64,0:05:10.01,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Serve me well, Ichigo.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.12,0:05:28.04,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What’re those guys doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.16,0:05:31.42,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Ichigo.\NAre you going home?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.68,0:05:33.72,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,We are also heading home now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.80,0:05:35.80,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Lady Rurichiyo!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.04,0:05:37.52,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Let us go together.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.00,0:05:39.43,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You’re going the same way?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.04,0:05:41.04,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.20,0:05:43.52,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh then, we’ll be together\Npart of the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.48,0:05:44.72,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Let’s go!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.95,0:05:46.68,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo, let us go!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.68,0:05:47.68,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,This will not do!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.08,0:05:52.79,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,We chose today’s route home\Nafter careful investigation.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.28,0:05:56.57,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,We cannot waste any time\Nlingering with others.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.28,0:05:58.45,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.88,0:06:01.96,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Please heed our request.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.24,0:06:05.61,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,No! I am going home with Ichigo!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.37,0:06:10.51,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I will buy you a sweet snack on\Nthe way home, so please bear with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.86,0:06:13.36,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,The sweets in this world\Nare delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.86,0:06:14.82,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.36,0:06:16.92,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo, I shall see you again!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.48,0:06:27.54,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Something’s up, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.16,0:06:30.09,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,They’re being way too careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.80,0:06:39.53,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You are a wonderful cook, Kenryu!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.53,0:06:40.74,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.13,0:06:43.88,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It has been a while since I had\Nas much fun as I did today.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.25,0:06:46.35,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m glad to hear that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.68,0:06:49.32,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Can I go to school again tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.72,0:06:51.39,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.39,0:06:53.92,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I’m looking forward to it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.72,0:06:58.10,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I can see Ichigo Kurosaki\Nagain tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.48,0:06:59.28,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.92,0:07:02.92,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Lady Rurichiyo, he is…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.44,0:07:05.14,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,He is a fine man.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.14,0:07:06.45,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,And strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.45,0:07:07.40,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,No, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.40,0:07:09.91,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You must not warm up\Nto him so easily!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.12,0:07:12.24,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,He is far beneath you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.64,0:07:15.88,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,If you become too close to him,\Nthere may be serious consequences!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.09,0:07:20.35,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Consequences?\NSuch as what?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.28,0:07:21.88,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Well…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.76,0:07:24.32,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That is…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.48,0:07:27.48,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I know. Both of you\Nare such worrywarts.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.92,0:07:30.37,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Now then,\NI shall have my dinner!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.52,0:07:31.30,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.80,0:07:33.81,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.64,0:07:40.27,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! The same class?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.84,0:07:42.04,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.04,0:07:42.95,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.48,0:07:45.64,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,They ingeniously used\NMemory Replacement
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.68,0:07:48.65,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,to transfer to our class\Nwithout raising any suspicion.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.90,0:07:53.03,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo, do you think they’re…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.56,0:07:57.20,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,There is no mistake that\Nthey have business with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.64,0:07:58.96,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,But if so, why?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.03,0:08:03.26,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Rukia… Weren’t you\Nchecking them out?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.68,0:08:07.82,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, but there was no sign\Nthat they used the Senkaimon.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.22,0:08:12.36,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,And that gigai,\NI’m certain it’s from Urahara.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.36,0:08:16.24,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,But they refuse to answer my questions,\Nclaiming it’s a trade secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.57,0:08:21.29,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,This is starting to smell very fishy!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.68,0:08:26.22,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo! Let’s sneak into their place\Nand find out once and for all!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.54,0:08:28.44,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Forget it, that’s a pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.44,0:08:31.69,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?! Why?\NAren’t you curious?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.60,0:08:34.87,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Urahara is leaving them alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.87,0:08:36.75,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,So there probably\Nisn’t anything wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.68,0:08:39.89,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,We all have our circumstances.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.17,0:08:42.14,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Let’s leave them alone for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.56,0:08:43.36,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.33,0:08:46.20,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You’re right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.41,0:08:51.04,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?! Aren’t you worried?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.04,0:08:54.04,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m so worried I can’t sleep!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.36,0:09:22.39,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.39,0:09:23.21,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s from next door!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.40,0:09:33.82,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it his Spiritual Pressure?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.44,0:09:37.51,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,In any case, this Spiritual Pressure\Nisn’t normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.88,0:09:38.86,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Let’s go, Rukia!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.86,0:09:41.36,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What’s the ruckus?\NCan’t a person sleep in peace?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.19,0:09:54.20,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You! What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.44,0:10:00.70,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Your Spiritual Pressure isn’t\Nthe same as earlier today.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.04,0:10:02.15,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What’s going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.82,0:10:06.61,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m a Substitute Soul Reaper,\Nso I can’t ignore this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.61,0:10:07.64,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Explain yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.15,0:10:09.32,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Otherwise…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.40,0:10:11.32,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.52,0:10:12.32,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s here!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.80,0:10:14.73,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! This Spiritual Pressure…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.32,0:10:19.26,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Why you…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.48,0:10:22.28,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.28,0:10:45.20,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Kenryu! Who is this guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.40,0:10:51.16,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo Kurosaki,\NI leave the rest to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.40,0:10:52.20,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.26,0:10:54.99,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.28,0:10:59.08,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,He ran off.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.28,0:11:00.40,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Those guys…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.52,0:11:11.82,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Just who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.36,0:11:14.49,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You don’t seem to be\Nfrom the Stealth Force.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.00,0:11:17.99,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.60,0:11:24.13,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Where do you think you’re going?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.36,0:11:28.27,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,So it’s Rurichiyo and\Nher men he’s after.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.40,0:11:31.67,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Seems that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.24,0:11:35.33,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you after\NRurichiyo and her guys?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.33,0:11:36.21,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Speak up!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.48,0:11:43.42,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.80,0:11:53.12,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that?!\NI lost consciousness for a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.92,0:11:54.92,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What’s the matter, Ichigo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.00,0:12:01.80,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Rukia!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.40,0:12:07.08,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell is that anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.44,0:12:09.51,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You mean his Zanpakuto’s power?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.21,0:12:14.44,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Watch out, Ichigo.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.76,0:12:16.61,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,The light reflected off from his blade…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.21,0:12:19.44,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s not just a smoke screen.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.56,0:12:20.88,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.91,0:12:28.66,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.40,0:12:31.40,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Don’t look at the light!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.32,0:12:34.32,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.84,0:12:40.14,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,His swordmanship…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.84,0:12:46.11,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you an assassin?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.86,0:12:47.95,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Assassin?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.44,0:12:51.52,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Rukia!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.76,0:12:55.88,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo! Capture him alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.24,0:12:58.69,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,We’ll make him tell us\Nwhy he’s after Rurichiyo!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.02,0:13:00.22,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.30,0:13:08.40,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.20,0:13:10.99,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.64,0:13:16.61,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo! Don’t look at the light!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.90,0:13:18.11,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep your eyes on the enemy!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.48,0:13:20.01,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Easy for you to say!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.56,0:13:25.54,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.64,0:13:44.90,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I can bring down a guy like you\Nwithout looking at your face.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.40,0:13:51.81,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Your Zanpakuto reflects\Nthe light from the moon
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.18,0:13:55.54,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,and it seems to knock out any opponent\Nwho looks at it for an instant.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.20,0:14:09.39,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,In order to do that, you must always\Ncome around to face me directly.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.80,0:14:11.04,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Once I figured that out…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.40,0:14:13.36,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, but you’re\Nno longer a challenge.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.76,0:14:15.82,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, you’re gonna talk!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.47,0:14:18.84,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you after\NRurichiyo and her men?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.32,0:14:23.36,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Answer!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.00,0:14:27.65,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Like I’ll let you get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.00,0:14:38.64,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.32,0:14:43.60,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Did he kill himself?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.06,0:14:44.96,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.10,0:14:50.77,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems Rurichiyo and her men\Nare involved in a dire situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.59,0:14:57.40,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I see you got rid of the assassin.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.07,0:14:59.74,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo Kurosaki,\NI must praise your good—
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.40,0:15:02.92,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that for?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.96,0:15:06.18,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That’s for running off\Nand leaving us to fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.68,0:15:08.89,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,This time, you will tell us\Nyour predicament.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.76,0:15:15.17,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll ask Inoue to come.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.16,0:15:18.32,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I should call Ishida and Chad too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.21,0:15:30.54,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Lady Rurichiyo Kasumiohji is…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.80,0:15:35.31,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Kasumiohji?\NAs in, the Kasumiohji Clan?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.84,0:15:37.62,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You know them, Kuchiki?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.96,0:15:41.05,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,They are high-ranking aristocrats\Nnext to the four great noble families.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.32,0:15:42.54,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.54,0:15:44.28,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Why didn’t you remember that
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.28,0:15:46.99,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,the first time you heard\Nthe name Kasumiohji?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.32,0:15:49.41,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Kuchiki… Kuchiki?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.94,0:15:52.96,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Kuchiki as in the Kuchiki Clan?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.21,0:15:54.77,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.08,0:15:57.28,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, forgive our rudeness!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.72,0:15:59.51,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I never imagined\NI’d find someone
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.51,0:16:01.44,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,belonging to the Kuchiki Clan\Nin a place like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.60,0:16:03.05,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,And you guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.05,0:16:07.44,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did it take you this long\Nto recognize the name, Kuchiki?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.70,0:16:12.42,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Kurosaki… Things won’t move forward\Nif you keep on questioning!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.84,0:16:14.38,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s not my fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.92,0:16:17.67,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,No need for the formality.\NDon’t bow.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.80,0:16:23.92,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Lady Rurichiyo is the legitimate heir\Nof the Kasumiohji Clan.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.40,0:16:29.40,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It would have been fine\Nif her parents,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.40,0:16:31.22,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,the previous heads of the family,\Nwere alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.74,0:16:38.32,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Lady Rurichiyo’s mother,\Nthe previous head of family,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.32,0:16:41.51,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,died shortly after giving birth to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.93,0:16:47.44,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Then her father immediately\Nfollowed in death from an illness.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.94,0:16:54.73,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,We have been her stewards since\Nshe was born, and we raised her.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.72,0:16:59.70,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,She hasn’t taken over as head\Nof the household yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.95,0:17:01.77,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,She was so young.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.08,0:17:05.13,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,We thought it better to wait\Nuntil she was older.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.88,0:17:07.77,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,But that turned into a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.48,0:17:12.16,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,There is a man\Nnamed Gyokaku Kumoi
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.16,0:17:15.63,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,who is currently the provisional\Nadministrator of the Kasumiohji Clan.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.85,0:17:22.24,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Lately, vassals have begun to\Ndisappear from his service.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.23,0:17:29.24,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems he gets rid of vassals\Nwho don’t agree with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.80,0:17:35.32,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,There are signs that Kumoi is\Ntaking advantage of his position
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.36,0:17:39.24,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,and is trying to take over\Nthe Kasumiohji Clan.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.24,0:17:41.40,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,A coup d’état?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.20,0:17:48.25,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,And recently, strange things have\Nbeen occurring around Lady Rurichiyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.24,0:17:59.24,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Don’t tell me…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.24,0:18:00.10,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.40,0:18:03.32,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Kumoi is finding Lady Rurichiyo,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.36,0:18:06.94,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,the legitimate heir to\Nthe Kasumiohji Clan, a hindrance.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.94,0:18:09.13,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Hence, the child’s assassination.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.44,0:18:10.44,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,How cruel.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.90,0:18:12.34,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have proof?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.82,0:18:17.40,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,We thought it was\Ntoo dangerous to ignore,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.40,0:18:19.24,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,so in order to\Nprotect Lady Rurichiyo…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.40,0:18:25.92,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,We didn’t tell even\Nthe closest vassals,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.92,0:18:27.42,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,and left under the cover\Nof the night mist.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.95,0:18:31.16,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,We passed through the Senkaimon
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.16,0:18:33.00,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,that is expressly for the use\Nof the Kasumiohji Clan
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.04,0:18:35.17,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,and escaped to\Nthe World of the Living.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.84,0:18:41.36,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That’s why the Soul Pager\Ncouldn’t find a record of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.92,0:18:43.48,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,As you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.52,0:18:47.87,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Soul Pagers cannot access data\Nrelating to private Senkaimon.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.44,0:18:52.88,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What’s wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.16,0:18:55.29,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo Kurosaki…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.72,0:18:58.27,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,We have heard of you,\Neven in Soul Society.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.27,0:19:01.22,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Your strength is amazing.\NI bore witness to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.56,0:19:02.36,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.72,0:19:06.42,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Assassins are certain to come\Nafter Lady Rurichiyo again.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.80,0:19:08.88,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,They belong to\Na special assassination squad
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.92,0:19:13.11,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,secretly assembled by Kumoi using\Nthe Kasumiohji Clan’s political influence.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.48,0:19:17.40,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo Kurosaki, please become\NLady Rurichiyo’s bodyguard!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.68,0:19:19.92,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hold on a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.92,0:19:20.87,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.52,0:19:25.12,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,If news of the strife within\Na noble family is made public,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.12,0:19:28.26,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,the Kasumiohji Clan\Nwill face disbanding.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.04,0:19:30.04,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That is why we\Ncannot appeal to
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.08,0:19:31.98,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,the Soul Reapers of\Nthe Thirteen Court Guard Squads!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.39,0:19:34.92,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Luckily, you are\Na Substitute Soul Reaper,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.52,0:19:37.04,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,not a legitimate Soul Reaper.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.09,0:19:39.36,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, but…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.36,0:19:40.29,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.72,0:19:44.42,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,We alone cannot defend\Nagainst Kumoi’s assassins!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.48,0:19:49.32,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What if we capture the assassin\Nand present him to Kumoi
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.32,0:19:50.64,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,as proof of his treachery?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.16,0:19:53.95,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,He will only deny\Nknowing the assassin.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.92,0:19:59.52,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, when they fail their mission,\Nthey commit suicide.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.16,0:20:01.48,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Furthermore,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.48,0:20:05.74,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,they use ominous techniques\Nand are extremely skilled.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.44,0:20:11.08,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo, do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.72,0:20:13.16,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll help too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.52,0:20:14.81,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Kuchiki, you too?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.00,0:20:16.93,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,We cannot possibly ask you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.93,0:20:19.84,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,No. I belong to the Kuchiki Clan.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.84,0:20:22.65,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I’ve experienced first-hand, the trials\Nand tribulations of an aristocratic family.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.65,0:20:23.63,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I cannot ignore your plight.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.96,0:20:28.51,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I have no choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.80,0:20:31.22,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.32,0:20:34.85,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,There’s one other thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.20,0:20:38.45,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Lady Rurichiyo is not aware\Nthat she is being targeted.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.75,0:20:41.05,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,And we don’t want her to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.24,0:20:44.52,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,We don’t want to hurt her\Nwith such knowledge.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.24,0:20:49.03,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Hence, we want her to remain totally\Nunaware of the real situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.48,0:20:51.23,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! That’s…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.56,0:20:52.59,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Forgive us!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.16,0:20:56.53,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Cripes…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.52,0:21:15.91,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Lost to a Substitute Soul Reaper?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.91,0:21:19.49,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. This Substitute Soul Reaper\Nseems to be very skilled.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.00,0:21:22.96,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Why would someone like\Na substitute aid the Princess?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.52,0:21:27.93,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,We must speed things up,\Nor there could be problems.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.04,0:21:32.42,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Very well. I’ll leave it to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.00,0:21:46.60,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Taking over a clan is quite a chore.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.29,0:23:22.68,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo, is it true that you’re\Ngonna be a bodyguard next?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.68,0:23:25.18,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Things turned out\Nthat way before I knew it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.18,0:23:28.74,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,All right! I don’t like the idea\Nthat it’s a small little girl,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.74,0:23:30.19,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,but I’ll do my very best too.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.19,0:23:31.27,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You can rely on me!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.27,0:23:32.77,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, you can stay\Nand watch the house.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.77,0:23:34.39,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,All right… What, again?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.15,0:23:36.23,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Illustrated Guide to Soul Reapers!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.23,0:23:37.33,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,– Yeah!\N– Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.88,0:23:38.18,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,MEN'S SOUL REAPER ASSOCIATION\NMEN’S LAVATORY
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.36,0:23:42.37,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Vice-President,\Nwhat is the agenda?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.37,0:23:45.07,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? You’re asking me?\NDid you forget the…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.62,0:23:49.75,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,We are discussing\Nthe Soul Pager today.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.75,0:23:52.18,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Quit that Hiroshima dialect.\NYou can’t even use it properly.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.40,0:23:56.14,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Men must have the special Soul Pager\Nwith twist-on headbands.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.14,0:23:58.01,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You too, idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.01,0:24:01.48,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s gotta be gold.\N	You can even embed jewels.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.03,0:24:03.84,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,MANUFACTURED BY\NOMAEDA JEWLRLY (LIMITED)
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.48,0:24:03.92,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Too expensive! Don’t advertise\Nyour own family business, idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.00,0:24:05.01,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,TO BE CONTINUED